{"tid":229152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙程賊甫抵港 扑女子頭搶手機","createTime":"2017-05-04T11:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T12:22:51.000Z","uid":96644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"802b1025378b947c4c4ef161ed2a2f6df39149eb","tid":229152,"uid":96644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:54:09.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】專程來港犯案的「雙程賊」，昨在東鐵紅磡站剛下車，便趁一名女子邊行邊講電話，用硬物扑向其頭部，搶去一部價值五千元iPhone 7智能手機，兩名好心南亞漢睹狀，合力將疑犯制服交警拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，昨午二時二十分，在都會軒商場任職二十一歲姓李女子，上班途經停車場，被匿藏暗處戴鴨舌帽獨行賊伺機截劫，賊人用硬物從後扑向女事主，更將之推倒，搶走約值五千元的iPhone 7手機，隨即朝都會軒方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n李女頭部輕傷站起身，尾隨追截並高呼「搶野」，其時兩名南亞漢在附近一輛房車上休息，發現女事主高呼求救，見義勇為下車尾隨追賊，最後合力將疑匪按地制服。其中一名四十三歲南亞勇漢報案，警方接報趕至調查後，以涉嫌行劫拘捕涉案三十歲姓李內地漢，揭發有人剛持雙程證從內地入境，甫抵埗便即時找尋目標搶劫。<br />\n<br />\n李女頭及手腳擦傷，疑犯亦聲稱背痛不適，兩人同送往伊利沙伯醫院治療，稍後出院，與兩名協助擒賊南亞漢同返警署，警方將案暫列行劫，目前調查疑犯來港有多少次，會否有同黨及牽涉其他同類案件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d47f54d8036f47d65f208630e0a5f9b887d983","tid":229152,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"蝗vs蝻<br />\n今鋪點拆好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f29c5f406c3ae76982708ac0df733f3730699a0","tid":229152,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:58:02.000Z","msg":"緊係扑尻你 截左佢地糊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734da8486f9cd17c1a4f210017478eae0379450e","tid":229152,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係扑尻你 截左佢地糊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n答案正確"},{"pid":"eb4a3dca7f84f2d753e8806a6e2ac05cfabc9ef5","tid":229152,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係扑尻你 截左佢地糊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI MEAN幫手禁尻住個蝗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da38311bd2bd8674ddd142b6dbba1c40161a5e44","tid":229152,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:00:35.000Z","msg":"強國專才湧港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2aa5b989d1c26ce0cb7f5f16b3b25f8fb7a9505","tid":229152,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係扑尻你 截左佢地糊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1ec94f8da3e0e30408c9149a11692c0c4d8972","tid":229152,"uid":96644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:21:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝗vs蝻<br />\n今鋪點拆好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係黑吃黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4244b7be957d3a9cbedf2cd2671d1ead3ef1bc4b","tid":229152,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"睇結果,蝗輸"}]}